With TF v1.2.1 I have to use:

from tensorflow.contrib.keras.python.keras.layers.wrappers import TimeDistributed

@fchollet It looks like the import did not make it into the latest release, but is in master: https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/v1.2.1/tensorflow/contrib/keras/api/keras/layers/__init__.py
body:
With TF v1.2.1 I have to use:
```
from tensorflow.contrib.keras.python.keras.layers.wrappers import TimeDistributed
```

@fchollet It looks like the import did not make it into the latest release, but is in master: https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/v1.2.1/tensorflow/contrib/keras/api/keras/layers/__init__.py
